.subsubsection Side Panels

.imagetext basicconcepts/side_panel.png

.nobullets
.item This is a container that can be hidden or resized  and its handles can face sideways, downwards or upwards.

.item It is hidden or shown when the user clicks on one of the two small arrow buttons displayed on its border.
.item  It is resized when the users clicks on the border between the buttons, and moves the mouse. 

.end imagetext


